{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WorkerGlobalScope: languagechange イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/fonts\"><code>fonts</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>self</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>dump()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\"><code>importScripts()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><em><code>languagechange</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/offline_event\"><code>offline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/online_event\"><code>online</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>languagechange</code></strong> イベントは、ユーザーの推奨言語が変更されたときにグローバルスコープオブジェクトで発生します。</p>\n<p>このイベントはキャンセル不可で、バブリングしません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このイベント名を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> などのメソッドで使用するか、イベントハンドラープロパティを設定するかしてください。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">onlanguagechange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベント型","title":"イベント型","isH3":false,"content":"<p>一般的な <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>languagechange</code> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener</code></a> メソッドで使用することができます。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>worker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange event detected!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>または、 <code>onlanguagechange</code> イベントハンドラープロパティを使用します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>worker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onlanguagechange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'languagechange event detected!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-langu